				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody"><span style="font-style: italic">inspired by suggestions in the Damage Shield thread</span>
<br />

<br />
How about elemental wards that give differing beneficial effects (in the short buff window) based on the element:
<br />

<br />
Fire :  damage shield (that stacks) - Fire resist
<br />
Water : HP or Mana Regen - maybe overhaste /  Poison Resist
<br />
Air : dodge / AC / Cold Resist
<br />
Earth : AC / Parry / Disease Resist
<br />

<br />
These could be added at lower levels with lower effects - adding new utililty to the mage at all levels.<br />_________________<br />Vermi Pejoratus - magician
<br />
Belhaven - priest of Innoruuk
<br />
Member of <a href="http://www.championsinarms.com/" target="_blank" class="postlink">Champion In Arms</a> on Quellious</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
